{"lemma":"أَصْحَرَيْ","slug":"أَصْحَرَيْ","root":"ص.ح.ر","root_slug":"ص-ح-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ص-ح-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23795","n23808"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%B5%D9%92%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to go into the desert"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be wide, vast"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be blind on one eye, to be one-eyed"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23795","headword_ar":"اصحر","root":"SHr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, Mgh, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ASHr AlS~aHoraA='a","text_ar":"اصحر الصَّحْرَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, [but I think that this is a mistake for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ASHr A_ilaY AlS~aHoraA='i","text_ar":"اصحر اـِلَى الصَّحْرَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iSoHaArN","text_ar":"اـِصْحَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He went forth to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SHrA='","text_ar":"صحرا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desert,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.], (S, A, Mgh,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SHrA='","text_ar":"صحرا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Msb, K:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tSH~r","text_ar":"تصحّر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in this sense] has not been heard. (Mgh.) ―         -b2-  Hence, in a trad., the saying of Umm-Selemeh to 'Áïsheh,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sak~ana A@ll~`hu EuqayoraAki falaA tuSoHiriyhaA","text_ar":"سَكَّنَ ا@للّٰهُ عُقَيْرَاكِ فَلَا تُصْحِرِيهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning, accord. to explanations of it in the TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eqr","text_ar":"عقر"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"God hath made thy dwelling and estate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or, as Z explains it,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thy person"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafosaki","text_ar":"نَفْسَكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be quietly settled, therefore do not thou remove it forth to the desert"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tuboriziyhaA A_ilaY AlS~aHoraA='i","text_ar":"لَا تُبْرِزِيهَا اـِلَى الصَّحْرَا=ءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the verb, accord. to IAth, being made trans. by"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1654},{"kind":"text","text":"the suppression of the prep.; [i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuSoHiriyhaA","text_ar":"تُصْحِرِيهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"being for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuSoHiriY bihaA","text_ar":"تُصْحِرِى بِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":";] for it is [properly] intrans. (TA. [See also the next sentence but one, in which the verb is tropically made trans.]) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSoHiro liEaduw~ika","text_ar":"اَصْحِرْ لِعَدُوِّكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Be thou in a state of clearness"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"certainty"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with respect to the case of thy enemy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JM, TA:) occurring in a trad. of 'Alee. (TA.) ―         -b4-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSoHara biAlA^amori","text_ar":"اَصْحَرَ بِالاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSoHarahu","text_ar":"اَصْحَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He revealed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made manifest, the affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA tuSoHiro A^amoraka","text_ar":"لَا تُصْحِرْ اَمْرَكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Reveal not thy affair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSoHirohu bimaA fiY qalobika","text_ar":"اَصْحِرْهُ بِمَا فِى قَلْبِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Reveal to him what is in thy mind"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ASHr","text_ar":"اصحر"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a place,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, wide,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spacious;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it became like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHoraA='","text_ar":"صَحْرَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-  Said of a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, blind of one eye."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","Mgh","K","Msb","JM","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n23808","headword_ar":"اَصْحَرُ","root":"SHr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Of the colour termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHorap","text_ar":"صُحْرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"similar to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSobaHN","text_ar":"اَصْبَحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (As:) a man"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a red colour inclining to dust-colour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having a colour such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uqorap","text_ar":"شُقْرَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon his head:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(As:) and an ass"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which is a red colour:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a dust-colour with redness:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which is whiteness and redness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHuwrN","text_ar":"صَحُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a she-ass; or this signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wont to kick with her hind leg:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SaHoraA='u","text_ar":"صَحْرَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) and pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHorN","text_ar":"صُحْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SuHaAriY~N","text_ar":"صُحَارِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^aSoHaru","text_ar":"الاَصْحَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmuSoHiru","text_ar":"المُصْحِرُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The lion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh, K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","As","TA","A"]}]}}